import React from 'react'
import { UserProvider } from './Context'
import {BrowserRouter} from "react-router-dom"
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'


const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <BrowserRouter>
      <UserProvider>
        <App />
      </UserProvider>
    </BrowserRouter>
  </React.StrictMode>
)
